<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.8.7">
<l>nāṭi yeṉṟa ṉuḷḷaṅ koṇṭa nāta ṉeṉṟum nāṉ maṟaikaḷ</l>
<l>tēṭi yeṉṟuṅ kāṇa māṭṭāc celva ṉeṉṟuñ ciṟaikoḷ vaṇṭu</l>
<l>cēṭu lavu poḻilkoḷ nāṅkait tēva tēva ṉeṉṟeṉ ṟōti</l>
<l>pāṭa kañcēr mella ṭiyāḷ pārttaṉ paḷḷi pāṭu vāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying, “Lord who, seeking [me], took my heart,”</l>
<l>Saying, “Noble who is never able to be seen</l>
<l rend="indent">[by] searching the four Vedas,”</l>
<l>Reciting over and over, “God of gods in Nāṅkai with groves</l>
<l rend="indent">where winged bees stir in a mass,”</l>
<l>The one with soft ankleted feet sings of Pārttaṉpaḷḷi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
